#Question 7: Set Difference and Intersection
#Problem Statement:Find the intersection and difference between two sets
A = {1, 2, 3, 4}
B = {3, 4, 5, 6}

intersection = A & B
difference = A - B

print("Intersection:", intersection)
print("Difference:", difference)
     #output
Intersection: {3, 4}
Difference: {1, 2}
